Title: Dedicates a portion of the state highway system to "CW2 and New York State Trooper John M. Grassia III"
Summary: Dedicates exit 25-A on I-90 to "CW2 and New York State Trooper John M. Grassia III".
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the highway law, in relation to dedicating a portion of the state highway system to "CW2 and New York State Trooper John M. Grassia III"
